    <keyword>TCP-ACO</keyword>
    <abstract>
      <t>This memo is suggests a pair of TCP options to allow use of alternate data checksum algorithms in the TCP header.  The use of these options is experimental, and not recommended for production use.  Note: This RFC corrects errors introduced in the editing process in RFC 1145.</t>
    </abstract>
